{"tid":2084803,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"支國癲到連數學論文都造假，犀利到連數學公式都虛構埋","createTime":"2020-06-29T13:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T15:12:45.000Z","uid":48040,"like":424,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"16541d857dd6b2b7348c2e29ae44c84250249969","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"國外一個關注學術誠信的網站For Better Science近日有人發布調查報告，發現有一批中國學者系統性地相互抄襲。而更加令人驚訝的是，<span style=\"color: orange;\">這些中國學者的論文中，連數學公式都虛構，甚至虛構出一個外國的共同作者，以增加自己論文的可信度。</span><br />\n<br />\n其實一般來講，發表係學術期刊上面的論文，都會經過同行（即係其他學者）的評審。但呢班中國學者，虛構出一堆不存在的外國專家及外國參考論文。評審者可能都被嗰一連串外國專家的名字嚇親，又或者係純粹懶，居然「睇唔出」裡面用的數學公式是虛構的，就讓呢D論文過關。<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌抄襲及虛構數學公式的論文（部分）：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dKPMCf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dKPMCf.png&h=8be2364e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forbetterscience.com/2020/06/15/beggers-test-for-schrodingerean-predator-prey-system/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforbetterscience.com%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2Fbeggers-test-for-schrodingerean-predator-prey-system%2F&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=e24b1420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forbetterscience.com/2020/06/15/beggers-test-for-schrodingerean-predator-prey-system/</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時都話，係作假呢件事上，支國從未讓我們失望！<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_OtH-ee5lSw&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=e2fadf76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw</a>"},{"pid":"411eeda60f2b1578c1d10ae3930bec8b67e07bca","tid":2084803,"uid":183758,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:10:41.000Z","msg":"越嚟越喺自爆嘅路上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b271b2354af75994341b2e52d89d0c6bc6df49c","tid":2084803,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec12e46d85c19cf4822224e772b5502f8cd9244","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":227,"dislike":1,"score":226,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"以後數學公式唔記得，自己作一個！<br />\n老師話唔得的話，就向教育局投訴：點解中國可以香港唔得？係咪搞分裂？"},{"pid":"ab5e236c986c23730410368f4e07f13c0c006450","tid":2084803,"uid":274870,"like":139,"dislike":0,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"啲中国人真係好叻利用呢啲漏洞，<br />\n睺準好多人唔會逐樣慢慢睇，<br />\n寫到天花龍鳳都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48976106b0944a5c21f48b80e941164571f6671e","tid":2084803,"uid":331421,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"啲式都虛構到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24077668e7baa2e4ed1d5a5e738df78da353046d","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"48976106b0944a5c21f48b80e941164571f6671e","tid":2084803,"uid":331421,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"啲式都虛構到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"只有想不到，只有做不到"},{"pid":"485f2a0dd408f660ad0880bccd454ffd11847fac","tid":2084803,"uid":26770,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"ab5e236c986c23730410368f4e07f13c0c006450","tid":2084803,"uid":274870,"like":139,"dislike":0,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"啲中国人真係好叻利用呢啲漏洞，<br />\n睺準好多人唔會逐樣慢慢睇，<br />\n寫到天花龍鳳都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"最大問題係中國的人才政策<br />\n出論文送樓有握手費<br />\n<br />\n學術期刊係睇出係邊,好多根本無q人睇"},{"pid":"b52fda98ce33723172a589fcc64a9912aa670f23","tid":2084803,"uid":241399,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"然後中國人又用返自己啲論文<br />\n唔怪得中國既野會爆炸"},{"pid":"b08b3d8af5231ca79e5192958781ae87e8aa8ba5","tid":2084803,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"利害"},{"pid":"5adba2f4d15efa92d0ff63a77d4138efa42a9e9d","tid":2084803,"uid":7609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"因為終國咩都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f271a87957ae6afd6a7ca94760dab215eb83a95","tid":2084803,"uid":279963,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲中国人真係好叻利用呢啲漏洞，<br />\n睺準好多人唔會逐樣慢慢睇，<br />\n寫到天花龍鳳都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>最大問題係中國的人才政策<br />\n出論文送樓有握手費<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">學術期刊係睇出係邊,好多根本無q人睇</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出左冇人睇係另一回事.<br />\n最大問題係學術界而家全部係講鬥出得多paper.<br />\n今時今日要入tenure track, (depend on which field), 有d field係講緊要有20+ papers先可以o係top tier university有機會. 所以無論係phd學生, postdoc, 定係後生教授, 都係要不斷submit papers.<br />\n咁就導致每個conference o既committee members (好多members都係一人o係N個conference committee入面) 每次要review好多papers.<br />\n<br />\n有professor係會畀自己phd學生去review paper, 自己唔去睇. 又有professor係每份paper只花最多5-10分鐘去睇. 甚至有部份paper佢係連5分鐘都冇.<br />\n所以reviewers係冇可能有時間睇晒成個methodology section. 好多時睇下abstract, 覺得佢講得頭頭是道, 就會決定accept/reject."},{"pid":"36bc83b2a2885e79ed3a8052d401dc076c31a8b6","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"b965097affa1312719319f5584f0becca0c37f1f","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1f271a87957ae6afd6a7ca94760dab215eb83a95","tid":2084803,"uid":279963,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲