lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0baac8f1dfc272c5989240840cc1a488f6d5e717","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:31:14.000Z","msg":"爭取「數學公式可以亂寫」加入附件三"},{"pid":"cb122ed4a455beb3a51051b9caae3c4e2fe1b246","tid":2084803,"uid":101110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fa0db6b72d593e7222185123df31f15570ca8efd","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"e3804907b3e088767803bab59acc50d26e797989","tid":2084803,"uid":101110,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"成個國家都不學無術，遇到有識之士就強加逼害。一棟摩天大廈嘅基根本打唔好，就用屍體一個個疊上去做底。<br />\n<br />\n啲平民命平過水泥鋼筋，有事咪埋返啲人肉人血做base頂住先，頂到幾耐我唔知，反正人命又用唔完嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"但德國總理默克爾居然仲讚賞中國，話中國係靠創意取得經濟成就"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"問佢一條問題，依家要佢揀，作為政治人物，代步德國車定中國車先講。<br />\n<br />\n咁又係幾有創意，呃到歐美幾十年油水，大家有錢齊齊賺。<br />\n<br />\n成個歐盟睇德國頭（號稱），佢哋只係唔妥Trump成日大美國主義，做盟友都要對歐盟行保護主義，一定唔妥Trump。但歐盟或者德國會唔會真係撐中國，事實上又唔見得。到底係放吓風俾美國咪再大美國主義俾啲面殘存嘅歐盟抖抖氣，定真係要做中國盟友，都仲存在好大走動空間。"},{"pid":"47327862ed99087e89d82ee6fb80ff4991b08f11","tid":2084803,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:35:51.000Z","msg":"數學都有得造假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe9ecba4e2c81740b977b6decbed5bfcb5734d6","tid":2084803,"uid":24788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"對世界來講係好事<br />\n中共會高估自己實力"},{"pid":"264bef4a38391305044c966c40a13b4f1ac55167","tid":2084803,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3804907b3e088767803bab59acc50d26e797989","tid":2084803,"uid":101110,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"成個國家都不學無術，遇到有識之士就強加逼害。一棟摩天大廈嘅基根本打唔好，就用屍體一個個疊上去做底。<br />\n<br />\n啲平民命平過水泥鋼筋，有事咪埋返啲人肉人血做base頂住先，頂到幾耐我唔知，反正人命又用唔完嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"yep 跟住咩都封殺 小粉紅繼續信黨媒 <br />\n由上到下都係思想有問題"},{"pid":"f33f157e936208fc59c2acd954d30e2d19192492","tid":2084803,"uid":50088,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"1f271a87957ae6afd6a7ca94760dab215eb83a95","tid":2084803,"uid":279963,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲中国人真係好叻利用呢啲漏洞，<br />\n睺準好多人唔會逐樣慢慢睇，<br />\n寫到天花龍鳳都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>最大問題係中國的人才政策<br />\n出論文送樓有握手費<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">學術期刊係睇出係邊,好多根本無q人睇</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出左冇人睇係另一回事.<br />\n最大問題係學術界而家全部係講鬥出得多paper.<br />\n今時今日要入tenure track, (depend on which field), 有d field係講緊要有20+ papers先可以o係top tier university有機會. 所以無論係phd學生, postdoc, 定係後生教授, 都係要不斷submit papers.<br />\n咁就導致每個conference o既committee members (好多members都係一人o係N個conference committee入面) 每次要review好多papers.<br />\n<br />\n有professor係會畀自己phd學生去review paper, 自己唔去睇. 又有professor係每份paper只花最多5-10分鐘去睇. 甚至有部份paper佢係連5分鐘都冇.<br />\n所以reviewers係冇可能有時間睇晒成個methodology section. 好多時睇下abstract, 覺得佢講得頭頭是道, 就會決定accept/reject."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n之前有藥廠做左個研究話就算登左係頂級論刊(nejm lancet)<br />\n有成七八成論文都係reproduce唔到論文嘅結果<br />\n全部都係圍內亂吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後警告再有咁嘅野就開名屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最搞笑呢個&ldquo;reproduce唔到結果嘅研究&rdquo;係reproduce到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffb3dd1af1ae4ffc8389e17d50d9b1e2d2f4074","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4fe9ecba4e2c81740b977b6decbed5bfcb5734d6","tid":2084803,"uid":24788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"對世界來講係好事<br />\n中共會高估自己實力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"如果呢D數學論文得出的結論，係起大壩或者整火箭嗰時用到就好啦"},{"pid":"ae33a26de9999c314ecfac2dd0c92d99a87400f8","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"智商唔夠，作假來救"},{"pid":"b00c8d6927115756b0830f17bac75c581d091795","tid":2084803,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16541d857dd6b2b7348c2e29ae44c84250249969","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"國外一個關注學術誠信的網站For Better Science近日有人發布調查報告，發現有一批中國學者系統性地相互抄襲。而更加令人驚訝的是，<span style=\"color: orange;\">這些中國學者的論文中，連數學公式都虛構，甚至虛構出一個外國的共同作者，以增加自己論文的可信度。</span><br />\n<br />\n其實一般來講，發表係學術期刊上面的論文，都會經過同行（即係其他學者）的評審。但呢班中國學者，虛構出一堆不存在的外國專家及外國參考論文。評審者可能都被嗰一連串外國專家的名字嚇親，又或者係純粹懶，居然「睇唔出」裡面用的數學公式是虛構的，就讓呢D論文過關。<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌抄襲及虛構數學公式的論文（部分）：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dKPMCf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dKPMCf.png&h=8be2364e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forbetterscience.com/2020/06/15/beggers-test-for-schrodingerean-predator-prey-system/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforbetterscience.com%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2Fbeggers-test-for-schrodingerean-predator-prey-system%2F&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=e24b1420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forbetterscience.com/2020/06/15/beggers-test-for-schrodingerean-predator-prey-system/</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時都話，係作假呢件事上，支國從未讓我們失望！<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_OtH-ee5lSw&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=e2fadf76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"樓主危害國家安全,我報左警<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4220e37a29fce12b946fa0dd455ee12733e94938","tid":2084803,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"看果個唔會有時間同你一頁一頁看<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752be06827e50eb5b04d201974e93fd505683139","tid":2084803,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"推 我地印咗15000張貼紙同大家分享國安法嘅喜悅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077616</a>"},{"pid":"5aa1d06bd2385358248cb1ff9f8639f5bc28c5be","tid":2084803,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4352051831898fb235d3b8025dce01eae02882","tid":2084803,"uid":34525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"FYP咩屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67708b4bec7915768abc55f9710bf4a67f6d210","tid":2084803,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb122ed4a455beb3a51051b9caae3c4e2fe1b246","tid":2084803,"uid":101110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fa0db6b72d593e7222185123df31f15570ca8efd","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"e3804907b3e088767803bab59acc50d26e797989","tid":2084803,"uid":101110,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"成個國家都不學無術，遇到有識之士就強加逼害。一棟摩天大廈嘅基根本打唔好，就用屍體一個個疊上去做底。<br />\n<br />\n啲平民命平過水泥鋼筋，有事咪埋返啲人肉人血做base頂住先，頂到幾耐我唔知，反正人命又用唔完嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"但德國總理默克爾居然仲讚賞中國，話中國係靠創