鬥出得多paper.<br />\n今時今日要入tenure track, (depend on which field), 有d field係講緊要有20+ papers先可以o係top tier university有機會. 所以無論係phd學生, postdoc, 定係後生教授, 都係要不斷submit papers.<br />\n咁就導致每個conference o既committee members (好多members都係一人o係N個conference committee入面) 每次要review好多papers.<br />\n<br />\n有professor係會畀自己phd學生去review paper, 自己唔去睇. 又有professor係每份paper只花最多5-10分鐘去睇. 甚至有部份paper佢係連5分鐘都冇.<br />\n所以reviewers係冇可能有時間睇晒成個methodology section. 好多時睇下abstract, 覺得佢講得頭頭是道, 就會決定accept/reject."},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:17:10.000Z","msg":"即係連學術界都未必做到fact check"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"咩未必<br />\n係因為大量做手腳<br />\n一早已經淪陷左<br />\n係學術界外嘅人唔知<br />\n或者圍內就好似dead body咁<br />\n死要扮到冇事或者有險可守<br />\n<br />\n早兩年hku都有支那prof柒撚左啦<br />\n咪又當冇事<br />\n<br />\n又有大量外國paper有支那名<br />\n我就信唔撚過嘢<br />\n乜撚野zhang, hao, sai 唔知乜鳩姓<br />\nCls"},{"pid":"8a63328be5127c9778ee4dd8c4f5574c498cd6fb","tid":2084803,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"呢D垃圾文都唔方去到decent journal <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e862bd709e8faadaaf810e41c256e31b789c969","tid":2084803,"uid":48040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:20:55.000Z","msg":"幫推twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1277617994219130880?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1277617994219130880%3Fs%3D20&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=a26e8fd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1277617994219130880%3Fs%3D20&h=1df8cc03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1277617994219130880?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"a306dc8eeb33c80cc7783dc33a14d207ca755d64","tid":2084803,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48976106b0944a5c21f48b80e941164571f6671e","tid":2084803,"uid":331421,"like":50,"disli